name: @riboseinc/paneron-extension-iec60417-symbols
description: Paneron extension for working with IEC 60417 symbols registry
author: Ribose Inc. <open.source@ribose.com>

scripts.build: rm -r compiled dist; mkdir compiled dist; tsc --outDir compiled; babel compiled --out-dir dist; cp package.json dist/; rsync -a --include '*/' --include '*.d.ts' --include '*.js.map' --exclude '*' compiled/ dist/
